---

<section class="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Built for Modern Microscopy</h2>
      <p class="section-description">
        Powerful microscopy control tools that integrate seamlessly into your Python workflow.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Hardware Sequencing</h3>
        <p class="feature-description">
          Advanced hardware-triggered sequences deliver precise timing and high-speed acquisition for demanding experiments.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/>
            <path d="M21 12c0 4.97-4.03 9-9 9s-9-4.03-9-9 4.03-9 9-9c1.09 0 2.13.2 3.1.56"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Type-Safe APIs</h3>
        <p class="feature-description">
          Full type hints and modern Python patterns ensure reliable microscopy control with excellent IDE support.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/>
            <polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Pure Python</h3>
        <p class="feature-description">
          No Java dependencies or complex setup. Pure Python ecosystem that installs with pip and works everywhere.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M14.5 4h-5L7 7H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v9a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-3l-2.5-3z"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="13" r="3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Real-time Events</h3>
        <p class="feature-description">
          Rich signal/slot system and event handling for responsive microscopy applications with real-time feedback and control.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/>
            <polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">GUI Components</h3>
        <p class="feature-description">
          Pre-built Qt widgets and complete GUI applications for rapid development of custom microscopy control interfaces.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="feature-title">Extensible Engine</h3>
        <p class="feature-description">
          Customizable MDA engines with hooks for preprocessing, real-time analysis, and hardware-specific optimizations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #111827;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #64748b;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: #f8fafc;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    border-color: #2563eb;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #7c3aed);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .feature-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #111827;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .feature-description {
    color: #64748b;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .feature {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
